cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "Zotero Private Search"
abstract: >-
  Verifiably private semantic search for Zotero libraries. Runs entirely
  in a Docker container with kernel-level iptables egress blocking, so
  documents and queries cannot leave the local machine. Aimed at
  researchers handling sensitive material — indigenous knowledge
  interviews, IRB-bound human-subjects data, privileged legal materials,
  and unpublished manuscripts.
type: software
authors:
